        for (int row = 0; row < rows; row++) { for (int column = 0; column < columns; column++) { //doubleArray[row][column] = indArray.getDouble(row, column); DataTool.normalize(matrix.getFloat(column, row), 0.0d, Double.valueOf(width)); double value = matrix.getDouble(column, row); double valueCap = DataTool.normalize(matrix.getFloat(column, row), 0.0d, Double.valueOf(width)); doubleArray[row][column] = valueCap; } } return doubleArray; }
